data.description: This mid-century modern home with a pool has been beautifully renovated and is conveniently located within  minutes of downtown Sarasota, I-75 and Siesta Key. The kitchen is fully updated and appointed with new hardwood cabinets,  granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The living area flows into the family room, making it a spacious  area to entertain and features porcelain tile throughout. Both bedrooms are tucked to the right side of the home and  share an updated bathroom with new cabinets, fixtures and a walk-in shower. The second full bathroom can be accessed from the house or pool area through the garage. The backyard is perfect to host a BBQ with friends, complete with a  private pool and Tiki Bar equipped with a built in wood bar, TV and full size refrigerator. This home is situated on a corner lot with a large fenced-in backyard with a 15ft sliding gate. Roof was replaced in 2023.
